    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;The Dynamic Host Configuration Protocol for IPv6 (DHCPv6) specification defined two stateful options, IA_NA and IA_TA, but did not anticipate the development of additional stateful options.  DHCPv6 Prefix Delegation added the IA_PD option, which is stateful.  Applications that use IA_NA and IA_PD together have revealed issues that need to be addressed.  This document updates RFCs 3315 and 3633 to address these issues.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
